        "\n",
        "## Project Information\n",
        "\n",
        "| Aspect | Details |\n",
        "|--------|---------|\n",
        "| **Project Title** | Four Key Challenges in Volatility Modeling |\n",
        "| **Data Source** | Yahoo Finance (yfinance) |\n",
