        "\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Methodology Overview\n",
        "\n",
        "This analysis examines **four fundamental challenges** in financial volatility modeling:\n",
        "\n",
        "| Challenge | Method | Key Formula |\n",
        "|-----------|--------|-------------|\n",
        "| **1. Skewness** | Jarque-Bera test, Moment-based estimation | $S = \\frac{\\frac{1}{n}\\sum (r_i - \\bar{r})^3}{[\\frac{1}{n}\\sum (r_i - \\bar{r})^2]^{3/2}}$ |\n",
        "| **2. Outliers** | MAD (Median Absolute Deviation), IQR, Z-score | $MAD = \\text{median}(|r_i - \\text{median}(r)|)$ |\n",
        "| **3. Overfitting** | Train-test split (70-30), MSE comparison | $MSE = \\frac{1}{n}\\sum_{i=1}^n (y_i - \\hat{y}_i)^2$ |\n",
        "| **4. Multicollinearity** | VIF (Variance Inflation Factor) | $VIF_k = \\frac{1}{1 - R_k^2}$ |\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n"
