        "\n",
        "### Skewness\n",
        "$$S = \\frac{\\frac{1}{n}\\sum (r_i - \\bar{r})^3}{\\left[\\frac{1}{n}\\sum (r_i - \\bar{r})^2\\right]^{3/2}}$$\n",
        "\n",
        "### Outliers (MAD)\n",
        "$$MAD = \\text{median}(|r_i - \\text{median}(r)|)$$\n",
        "\n",
        "### Overfitting Detection\n",
        "$$MSE_{test} = \\frac{1}{m}\\sum_{i=1}^m (y_i^* - \\hat{y}_i^*)^2$$\n",
        "\n",
        "### Multicollinearity (VIF)\n",
        "$$VIF_k = \\frac{1}{1 - R_k^2}$$\n",
        "\n",
